{"tid":539763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[點計分好?] 警務處文書女助理虛報未婚 被判守行為","createTime":"2018-01-25T00:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T02:40:28.000Z","uid":136994,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"48628a89f90fb25944b815b7e1cc4f173a61135a","tid":539763,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:24:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57747820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57747820&d=H94%2BgzYnyCrPm1IqZrKhghOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1ddc5dfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57747820&h=091ea895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57747820</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180124/large/1516771619_282d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180124%2Flarge%2F1516771619_282d.jpg&h=628a5985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警務處文書女助理於2011年與內地漢結婚，翌年1月誕下兒子，惟她於同年3月遞交兒子的出生登記文件時卻自稱未婚。至去年入境處調查一宗假結婚案時揭發事件。女助理原被控在出生登記作虛假陳述罪，控方今撤控，改以簽保守行為處理，被告獲准以1,000元守行為12個月，期間不得再犯不誠實的行為。<br />\n<br />\n於警務處法醫科任職的被告周美廷（28歲）被指於2012年3月1日犯案。辯方今指被告月入1.4萬元，而當日遞交的登記表格資料實由被告家人填寫，被告僅簽署確認，由於當時她剛產子不久，精神狀態較差才出現誤會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔知呢個可唔可以計入休班警呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c87efa5b970fa3febbb54c9b358b855480681e0b","tid":539763,"uid":30939,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"你搵唔搵到警犬搵萬四蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯Aco黎啦，都唔算警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"